-- Ukraine Appoints Temporary Administrator for Lender Bazys
-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 2012-04-20T14:44:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-20/ukraine-appoints-temporary-administrator-for-lender-bazys.html
Ukraine’s central bank appointed a
temporary administrator to oversee lender PAT AKB Bazys for six
months.  Natsionalnyi Bank Ukrainy , based in the capital Kiev,
appointed Hanna Hontar to manage Bazys between April 23 and Oct.
23, the central bank said in a statement today on its website.
The NBU also imposed a three-month moratorium for creditors,
effective April 23. Bazys is based in Ukraine’s eastern city of
Kharkiv.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
